document_data.History:
Red ache could be encountered in the [[Underdark]].

Red ache was one of many diseases inflicted on the soldiers fighting in the [[Rotting War]] at the [[Fields of Nun]] in {{YearlinkName|902}}. Centuries later, some roving [[undead]] still carried the disease.{{Cite web/Perilous Gateways/The Trail of Tears:The Scourge of Pestilence}}

The [[Brotherhood of the Scarlet Scourge]], a [[monk|monastic]] order dedicated to the [[Orc pantheon|orc god]] of disease, [[Yurtrus]], was known to weaponize the red ache against its enemies.
